1928;;The Red Dance;;American;;Raoul Walsh;;Dolores del Río, Charles Farrell;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Red_Dance;;Tasia (Dolores del Río), a beautiful dancer lower class of Russia, falls heir to the throne Prince, Grand Duke Eugene (Charles Farrell), but only admired from a distance. At the outbreak of the Russian Revolution, the Duke falls in captivity and this allows Tasia be near him.